Usage: remove_from_collection [-help] <base_collection>
                              <object_collection_or_list> [-intersect]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
<base_collection>               # Base collection of objects (string, required)
<object_collection_or_list>     # Second collection of objects, or an object
                                # list (string, required)
-intersect                      # Provides intersection of base collection
                                # elements with second collection of
                                # objects/lists (bool, optional)